The rare disease a man suffers from
The American Nick Hess was suspected by his family to be an alcoholic, his wife even filming him when he was dizzy, he could barely stand up and his words were hard to understand.
Although the 35-year-old said he did not drink alcohol, it was apparent that he was intoxicated.
When she first accused me of being drunk without drinking, I thought she was crazy.
