What button will appear soon
Millions of Facebook users have become accustomed to the “Like” button, and now the representatives of the social network are preparing another one, the “Dislike”.
Tuesday, Mark Zuckerberg, co-founder and CEO of the company, announced on the account or that this button will be available soon, the New York Times informs on the blog.
